ted children’s service</xref>, accessible from both indoor and outdoor play areas; and</li><li id="_c8c7924b-7e14-48da-b740-527921c54d3c">in an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1251_2.4.0.xml#_9ff8fad7-8992-4708-be17-784d962a0530" id="_2b6a5b80-5de7-493a-a600-7f7d8433aef5" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">early childhood centre</xref>, other than a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/2498_5.2.0.xml#_50885e6b-a68c-4be0-a0c4-ab94fbf8b27b" id="_849bbfc4-056c-4d66-a42e-ec7cc1623a53" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">restricted children’s service</xref>, the closet pans must be located in relation to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/10621_0.4.0.xml#_1856d29f-7649-45dd-8439-d52fd65d03a4" id="_b075e1aa-e216-4459-ba68-8d34769f5f49" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">children’s rooms</xref> and outdoor play spaces so that children using toilets can be observed by staff from <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/10621_0.4.0.xml#_1856d29f-7649-45dd-8439-d52fd65d03a4" id="_bcac2358-8236-436c-a030-9810dda1790c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">children’s rooms</xref> and outdoor play space.</li></ol></desc-note></table-variation></table-reference>